                       Sample sample,
                       Currencies currency)
                throws java.io.IOException

        Parameters:
        doc - the Jsoup document sampled from the exchange source, containing the full html or text content from which to sample data
        sample - The previously created Sample object to be populated with currency data
        currency - the currency to sample
        Returns:
        A fully populated Sample object with currency data for this exchange
